//   factor = Log factor to use.  Values of X are returned `factor` times more often than X+1.
function log_rand(minval, maxval, factor) = -ln(1-rands(1-1/pow(factor,minval), 1-1/pow(factor,maxval), 1)[0])/ln(factor);


