// Module: skew_xy() / skew_z()
//
// Description:
//   Skews children on the X-Y plane, keeping constant in Z.
//
// Usage:
//   skew_xy([xa], [ya]) ...
//   skew_z([xa], [ya]) ...
//
// Arguments:
//   xa = skew angle towards the X direction.
//   ya = skew angle towards the Y direction.
